==English==

===Noun===
'''[[tartare]] [[sauce]]'''
# A [[sauce]] made from [[mayonnaise]] and a [[chopped]] [[mixture]] of [[pickled]] [[gherkin]]s, [[caper]]s, [[olive]]s and [[shallot]]s; traditionally served with [[fish]].

